@node wiedza
- you can change a defalut graphic to any from a BONUS drawer
- you can define your own object trajectories. For example:

1112223322223344543322222222
0000011111122222222111111111
1111222333344455544433322222

You find it in progdir:gfx/trajectories
First line determines an acceleration in pixel for specified frame on X axis
Second line shows a frame displayed at this time.
Thrid line is a Y axis.

Black colour in graphic is a transparent colour. Brushes has a their own transarent 
colour defined in any graphic program.
@endnode
